                           <p>278 folios (+ 3 unfoliated paper flyleaves at the beginning and 3 unfoliated paper flyleaves and 1 parchment flyleaf at the end). </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </foliation>
                        
                        
                        
                        <collation>
                           
                           
                           
